Rounded Basalt 4.5 cm in diameter with glassy chilled margin with rust.

Piece 1A is a fresh basalt with distinct 9 mm-thick glassy chilled margins with rust (2.5Y 3/2 and 10YR 8/4); piece 2A is a fresh basalt with zoning and distinct 1.4 to 2 cm glassy chilled margin and calcite vein with well developed  calcite crystals. Piece 3 is a part of glassy chilled margin with rust, calcite and large green minerals (hydrothermal alteration).
